[normal]Chas Roy-Chowdhury[bold]: It is also 
[normal]about 
[normal]national insurance.  That is really what the legislation is all about, as well.  There is a big disparity between the self-employed rate and the employee rate, which is driving this.  We need to be very careful, in terms of 
[normal]UK
[normal] competitiveness, where we are going.  Just to redress the balance, the ACCA published 12 tenets of taxation about four years ago, which is available on the ACCA website.  We have circulated it to this Committee in the past and would be very happy to do so again.
